==Useful Info==
'''Charred statues''' are stationary guard [[statue]]s found in certain [[Vehumet]] [[altar]] [[vault]]s. They attack by occasionally shooting small blasts of [[fire]] at you while you're in their [[line of sight]].

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*With fire resistance, their attacks should be negligible. 
*If you don't intend to worship Vehumet, there's no harm in simply bypassing these.

[[Category:Vault-only monsters]]
